<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="SafeTech - Enterprise-Grade Premium Laptop Insurance for Emerging Markets">
  <title>SafeTech - Premium Laptop Insurance</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/premium.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-content">
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Enterprise-Grade <span class="highlight">Device Protection</span> for Emerging Markets</h1>
      <p>SafeTech provides innovative, affordable laptop insurance solutions designed for emerging markets. Protect your investment with flexible monthly plans, instant claims processing, and 24/7 premium support.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">📊 Go to Dashboard</a>
        <% } else { %>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">🚀 Get Protected Now</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">🔐 Sign In</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">💻</div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="features" id="features">
  <h2>Why Choose SafeTech?</h2>
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>📱 Easy Registration</h3>
      <p>Sign up in minutes with our streamlined process. Add your laptops instantly and choose your coverage level.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>💰 Affordable Plans</h3>
      <p>Premium monthly subscriptions starting from just ZMW 50. No hidden fees, transparent pricing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>🛡️ Full Coverage</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive damage, theft, and loss protection available. Choose the plan that fits your needs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>⚡ Quick Claims</h3>
      <p>Submit and track your claims in real-time. Fast approval process with 24/7 support.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>🌍 Global Support</h3>
      <p>Premium customer service available round the clock. Multiple support channels for your convenience.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>✨ Peace of Mind</h3>
      <p>Rest assured your investment is protected. Industry-leading coverage and reliability.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="plans">
  <h2>Premium Insurance Plans</h2>
  <div class="plans-grid">
    <div class="plan">
      <h3>Essentials</h3>
      <p class="price">ZMW 50<span style="font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: var(--font-normal);">/month</span></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Water damage protection</li>
        <li>Up to ZMW 5,000 coverage</li>
        <li>Email support</li>
        <li>Monthly payment</li>
        <li>Easy claim submission</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan featured">
      <h3>💎 Premium</h3>
      <p class="price">ZMW 100<span style="font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: var(--font-normal);">/month</span></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Theft & damage protection</li>
        <li>Up to ZMW 15,000 coverage</li>
        <li>24/7 priority support</li>
        <li>Water & liquid damage</li>
        <li>Fast claim processing</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Premium</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan">
      <h3>Enterprise</h3>
      <p class="price">ZMW 150<span style="font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: var(--font-normal);">/month</span></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Complete coverage</li>
        <li>90% device value</li>
        <li>Loss protection</li>
        <li>Extended warranty</li>
        <li>Dedicated support</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how-it-works">
  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">1</span>
      <h4>Register</h4>
      <p>Create your SafeTech account</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">2</span>
      <h4>Add Laptop</h4>
      <p>Register your device details</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">3</span>
      <h4>Choose Plan</h4>
      <p>Select your coverage level</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">4</span>
      <h4>Pay Monthly</h4>
      <p>Simple, affordable subscriptions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">5</span>
      <h4>Get Protected</h4>
      <p>Coverage starts immediately</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials">
  <h2>Trusted by Thousands</h2>
  <div class="testimonial-grid">
    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
      <p>"SafeTech has given me peace of mind. Excellent service and fast claims processing!"</p>
      <p class="author">- John K.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
      <p>"Best insurance value for money. Highly recommend to anyone with expensive laptops."</p>
      <p class="author">- Sarah M.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial">
      <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
      <p>"Customer support is phenomenal. They helped me process my claim within days."</p>
      <p class="author">- David T.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

